…….. Warn Electricity Consumers against Energy Theft The management of Eko Electricity Distribution Company (EKEDC) Plc says it is committed to bridge the metering gap in its area of operations. Mr Adeoye Fadeyibi, Chief Executive Officer of EKEDC, who gave the assurance at a Customers’ Stakeholders’ Forum at the weekend in Lagos, urged its electricity consumers to be patient with the company.